Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:03.00,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:06.32,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是上回故事的後續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:09.34,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮士在和貓先生一起修行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著上啊亮士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  涼子她?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:26.15,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  我們繼續講述御伽銀行最大的危機
